headline: Countdown to Boston Properties (BXP) Q4 Earnings: A Look at Estimates Beyond Revenue and EPS
summary: Besides Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimates for Boston Properties (BXP), review projections for some of its key metrics to gain a deeper understanding of how the company might have fared during the quarter ended December 2025.
